      "name_en": "TRISS Probability of Survival",
      "required": "*",
      "type": "calculated",
      "formula": "1 / (1 + e^(-b))  where b = b0 + b1×RTS + b2×ISS + b3×年齢区分(AIS90係数使用)",
      "notes": "年齢・RTS・ISSのいずれかが不明の場合は計算しない。自動計算。"
